attributes.title: Ep. 1 - Jordy Gets a Box!
attributes.caption: 12-year-old Jordy Defective is on a mission to learn all about the world's most popular game--and maybe get into a match or two.
attributes.description: Having grown up on an island where no one can play Box Peek, 12-year-old Jordy Defective is on a mission to learn all about the world's most popular game--and maybe get into a match or two.
